This paper deals with recommender systems, which are often studied in the machine learning subfield of "Learning" (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper focuses on incremental learning from data streams, which is a common topic in "Information Retrieval" (cs.IR) and "Artificial Intelligence" (cs.AI). The use of ensemble methods is also relevant to "Data Structures and Algorithms" (cs.DS). Finally, the paper's focus on improving accuracy in recommendation systems could also fall under "Social and Information Networks" (cs.SI).
